description: The man who was showing Covid-19 symptoms admitting leaving his home to walk his grandfather's dog.
title: Coronavirus: Four jailed for breaching Isle of Man lockdown rules
title_page: Coronavirus: Four jailed for breaching Isle of Man lockdown rules - BBC News
maintext: They later discovered Skillicorn had gone to his grandfather's home to pick up his dog before driving to Port Grainagh beach to walk it for "two to three hours".
